**/appsettings.Production.json
**/appsettings.Local.json
**/*.apikey
*Topstep API Key*
*api_key*
*apikey*

# Keep the template (no secrets)
!**/appsettings.template.json

# Visual Studio
.vs/
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
